                        <h3 id="point-2-title">Get the most out of your fields – bigger, better yields </h3>
                        <p>Our models constantly adapt to the crop’s growth stage and to the changing conditions of the soil and weather. This enables AgrrX to provide crop-specific recommendations that help achieve maximal yield, field-validated to generate a 10% crop-yield enhancement.</p>
