                        <h3 id="point-3-title">Make farming sustainable again</h3>
                        <p>If we want our agricultural lands to continue producing the food we eat for many more years, we must start taking better care of our soils.<br>
 <br>
We optimize inputs and monitor the movement of water and agrichemicals in the soil to minimize environmental pollution and prevent leaching, runoff, and unnecessary resource expenditures.  <br>
</p>
