                            <div class="text-wrapper wow fadeInUp" id="f-0-text" style="visibility: visible; animation-name: fadeInUp;">
                                <div>
                                    <h4>Adaptive, variable-rate irrigation management &amp; automation</h4>
                                    <p>The AgrrX app figures out exactly how much to irrigate the field by providing an irrigation prescription that is constantly adapting to the changing field conditions.<br>
<br>
By factoring in thousands of data points from previous cases, we can predict water-uptake patterns, detect faulty irrigation systems and burst pipes, and improve the decision-making process.<br>
</p>
