                        </div>
                                                                                                        <div class="feature p-1 even">
                            <div class="image-wrapper hide-on-m" id="f-1-image">
                                <img src="./index_files/FieldSummary.png" alt="">
                            </div>
                            <div class="text-wrapper wow fadeInUp" id="f-1-text" style="visibility: visible; animation-name: fadeInUp;">
                                <div>
                                    <h4>Crop-specific management: Solving crop variability and risk </h4>
                                    <p>By analyzing crop growth against crop models, we can predict the crop’s needs and expected growth, can detect any deviation, and can identify early-stage field variability and non-uniformity of crop growth.<br>
 <br>
We provide crop-specific recommendations and send alerts about field segments that need attention due to potential risk from pests or diseases. <br>
<br>
Do your plants have problems? We’ll know before they do. <br>
</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                                                                                                        <div class="feature p-2">
                            <div class="image-wrapper hide-on-m" id="f-2-image">
                                <img src="./index_files/NutritionMobile.png" alt="">
                            </div>
                            <div class="text-wrapper wow fadeInUp" id="f-2-text" style="visibility: visible; animation-name: fadeInUp;">
                                <div>
                                    <h4>Optimized fertilizer management to reduce crop loss</h4>
                                    <p>We take crop loss very seriously; ensuring that nitrogen is available to crops when they most need it is one important step to reducing crop loss. <br>
<br>
We integrate crop models, satellite imagery, and weather forecast data alongside the soil data we analyze to optimize fertilizer availability and create crop-specific application recommendations. </p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                                                                                                        <div class="feature p-3 even">
                            <div class="image-wrapper hide-on-m" id="f-3-image">
